import { useState } from "react"; import { Select, InputNumber, Collapse, Input, Card } from "antd"; const { Option } = Select; const { Panel } = Collapse; export default function Sidebar() { const [parameters, setParameters] = useState({ max_tokens: 2048, temperature: 1, top_p: 1, min_p: 0, top_k: 50, presence_penalty: 0, frequency_penalty: 0, repetition_penalty: 1, }); return (
max_tokens
temperature
top_p
min_p
top_k
presence_penalty
frequency_penalty
repetition_penalty
); }
